{"tid":304961,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)笑八仙 轟天猛將1-3","createTime":"2017-07-01T10:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T13:06:46.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"030d0d49571be1248c34df3276e44213da1eb079","tid":304961,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d881c373\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4ebe8eea\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=23859577\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-dXjzPT2fJUU/VR_-zcvm4tI/AAAAAAAAaT8/6tBBb497QvY/s1600/The%2BEight%2BHilarious%2BGods%2B(1993).JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-dXjzPT2fJUU%2FVR_-zcvm4tI%2FAAAAAAAAaT8%2F6tBBb497QvY%2Fs1600%2FThe%252BEight%252BHilarious%252BGods%252B%281993%29.JPG&h=1d125208&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f3/%E8%BD%9F%E5%A4%A9%E7%8C%9B%E5%B0%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff3%2F%25E8%25BD%259F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%258C%259B%25E5%25B0%2587.jpg&h=55cf280f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/column/images/stories/114/2012/09/20120918filmExpendables2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F114%2F2012%2F09%2F20120918filmExpendables2.jpg&h=64523bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://cn.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20140728/photo/bkn-20140728045402188-0728_00862_001_01b.jpg?094038\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140728%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140728045402188-0728_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F094038&h=aa91d4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.民間廣為流傳的道教八仙的故事已是大家最膾炙人口的故事之一，本片在這八位神仙的原型基礎上加以演繹和誇張，上演了一部爆笑連連的無厘頭風格喜劇電影。影片眾星雲集，由關之琳、鄭少秋、吳君如、吳孟達、鄭丹瑞、黎彼得、劉洵、成奎安、溫兆倫等聯袂出演<br />\n<br />\n2.巴尼支付了原協議要求的三百萬美元以保障人質安全，但海盜卻坐地起價要求五百萬。岡納則打算直接交火，引致海盜傷亡。岡納隨後因為對被俘的海盜動用私刑，而引發與「陰陽」之間的鬥毆，最後為巴尼所制止，由於岡納太過暴躁，精神極不穩定，巴尼將之驅逐出隊...<br />\n<br />\n3.這支傭兵組成的突擊隊由巴尼（席維斯&middot;史特龍飾）領軍，經過激烈的槍戰，解救了中國富豪和戰壕（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾），最終陰陽（李連杰飾）負責把商人護送回中國，陰陽就此下場。<br />\n回美國後，隊員比利（連恩&middot;漢斯沃飾）說他打算退出，到法國和女朋友團聚。巴尼答應了他的要求。<br />\n接著，巴尼接到了一個中情局情報員「教堂先生」（布魯斯&middot;威利飾）的新任務：去一架墜落在阿爾巴尼亞的中國空軍運輸機上，取回保險箱裏的秘密物品。同時在「教堂先生」的推薦下，華裔女性的陳美琪（余男飾）加入隊伍..<br />\n<br />\n4.浴血幫領導人巴尼&middot;羅斯（席維斯&middot;史特龍飾）帶領著手下李&middot;聖誕（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）、岡納&middot;詹森（杜夫&middot;朗格林飾）和托爾&middot;羅德（蘭迪&middot;寇楚飾）襲擊一輛前往軍事監獄的列車，幫助巴尼的老友死亡醫生（衛斯里&middot;史奈普飾）出來。死亡醫生被救出後，獨自一人解決列車上的士兵，並讓列車失控直衝監獄、造成監獄大爆炸。死亡醫生接受了巴尼的招募，回到了浴血幫。之後一行人到索馬利亞執行一件軍火商的彈藥走私任務，在那與海爾&middot;凱撒（泰瑞&middot;克魯斯飾）會合後展開行動。當中巴尼驚訝地發現，負責走私的軍火商就是浴血幫初期的聯合創始人康拉德&middot;史東班克斯（梅爾&middot;吉勃遜飾），原本走上歪路的他應早被巴尼解決，沒想到還活著。康拉德發現巴尼等人後隨即上了直升機，拿狙擊槍重傷凱撒並投下炸彈攻擊他們，之後便離去...<br />\n<br />\n6 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dd1ceb51146f8ce18f7f9145937fd47d220fcf","tid":304961,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996e30b68875d0b251f46120adf10a7533ff2240","tid":304961,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f069ee63cdfda33a9865c8a4bc20b67cbf26041e","tid":304961,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e521d1aa7a54da401d6d7b290f088ab63c22dc","tid":304961,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10fb9894ca0c5d984b628340a2134f140040272","tid":304961,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}